content:
The path ahead is shrouded in mystery.  
To unveil the journey, you must take a step.  
Seek the sacred button—its power awaits.  
Whisper the word that opens the door: "PUSH."

The path ahead is shrouded in mystery,  
awaiting your touch. A sacred button lies  
before you, a key to unlock the ancient  
protocol. To embark on this journey,  
whisper the word that stirs the air—  
a simple command that awakens the arcane.  

Type "PUSH" to begin your quest.
